removePlugin#

 * Type: (name: string) => void

Remove the internal Rspack plugin, the parameter is the constructor.name of the
plugin.

For example, remove the internal webpack-bundle-analyzer:

export default {
  tools: {
    rspack: (config, { removePlugin }) => {
